description: The world's greatest breakfast food is finally here, and it's being made by only the very best in San Diego! Marcel has made the simple waffle into an art form, with their Brussels, Liege, or Savory waffles, and a remarkable selection of terrific toppings. For the finest gourmet waffles this side of the Atlantic, nobody compares to the magnificent Marcel!
name: Marcel Authentic Belgian Waffles
